      "captured_at": null,
      "author": null,
      "contributor": null,
      "rationale": "Phase 2/3 addition returning a sequence of pairwise diffs between consecutive versions rather than a separate full-history engine \u2014 reuses the same diff computation and caching, and supports volatility/staged-migration/audit queries a single A-to-Z diff would collapse away.",
